{"tid":1323080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[路障討論] 兩層高會唔會比一層難拆好多？","createTime":"2019-07-16T06:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T13:54:05.000Z","uid":53349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab5bac3d26ab9387e7306712db3b15ce70744a13","tid":1323080,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"假設我哋仲有物資砌路障，要唔要試下砌一排兩層高，代替傳統既每排得單層？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意到有啲玩家已經將路障包保鮮紙(?)加固，如果兩層都包哂膠，我諗已經可以代替埋遮陣黎擋胡椒，甚至擋到一兩野橡膠彈？<br />\n<br />\n補充：個人主張遠距離防守，唔存在路障妨礙我方視線問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c476ddfb31f0943f9a719a578017381c2f713fb","tid":1323080,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"開錯台，好快沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671513ce8de196427819124c3c336913eae08930","tid":1323080,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09a7be4122089765c48905ac37ddeccff420def4","tid":1323080,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf310ad51e100522bdf2046f1462c136b155f95d","tid":1323080,"uid":176840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"沙田唔係有兩排？"},{"pid":"05a32c9c04de6ac1f9edf6da156ad8cc6965bf2a","tid":1323080,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"就係見到如果單層，無論整幾多排，啲狗都係玩障礙賽咁輕鬆跨過<br />\n<br />\n所以就諗下要疊高佢，轉做雙層，思考下阻礙程度會唔會倍增<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}